  EventText: "You follow the piercing gaze of the hunter as he stares into the woods
    beyond. He notices your approach with a flinch, before explaining his ability
    to see through things. He is currently one of many heroes participating in a
    great hunt, but he has also looked much further and seen a greater prize in the
    future. \r"
